Hi people, this was made by the author I could not find but the video retains from the presentation of this modification I have the opportunity to make the modifications to use again and hopefully I will not be accused of stealing this modification. I only do good deeds for people who play Skyrim. I hope people will be happy again getting a very beautiful sword and so much about it that sword can be made at Blacksmith. Thx you to the user who has me to bring this mod back to Nexus.
Thank you daresun

There will be two downloads one with the sword and the other update to be able to craft these swords you will need to get both the first sword and then update.

If someone will be presenting this sword please put a video on the site where you can download this sword i will be very grateful for your help and maybe this will help find the author thank you again heartily TheKinari9
